Class MockProblemMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.groboclown.retval.monitor.ObservedMonitor<T>
      • net.groboclown.retval.monitor.MockObservedMonitor<ProblemContainer>
        • net.groboclown.retval.monitor.MockProblemMonitor
  • public class MockProblemMonitor
extends MockObservedMonitor<ProblemContainer>
    A mock check monitor, suitable for testing. Note that if used in a non-test environment, this has the potential to quickly consume lots of memory.
